<p>

Dave Barry's columns are published every Friday on
<a href = "http://www.herald.com/davebarry/">his Web site</a> at the Miami
Herald.  But if you can't wait
that long, you can use this page to generate one instead.

Read <a href = "about.shtml">"About AutoDave"</a> for more information about Dave and this site.

<p>


