<td colspan=2>
The full version of AutoDave requires you to fill in 20 blank spaces in order to
generate a column.  To try "AutoDave Lite", fill in the following five blank spaces,
which will be enough to generate the first paragraph to give you an idea of how it works.
Then you can scroll down to try the full version
of AutoDave.
</td>
</tr>
